{
  "stem": "3040.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I said, here they need work, and I want to work.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- and I got it right away.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "This was the only document that was not a false document, by the way, because it was a real document issued by the employment office.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, she didn't.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She-- she had-- has a different story.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I'll come to it in a minute.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When I presented the-- this paper, of course they hired me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And this company had a place, a-- a house, where they could accommodate people who worked in their factory but did-- did not live in the-- in the close vicinity.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They could accommodate them, you know, a room to sleep or to share with somebody.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they said, we have a-- a house for-- for our workers.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And if you don't have where to stay, you can stay there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I was-- I couldn't be happier than this.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "My wife stayed behind with this-- with this young man, with his family, and she was looking for a job through the papers.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "There were advertisements.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And she answered one ad that required a maid for-- a maid and a-- a governess for children.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "She reported it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It happened to be a German family, and they hired her.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And they took her into their house, and she was taking care of the children and cleaning the house, whatever was necessary.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So for a little while, we were-- we were secure.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And since we wanted to see each other, Sunday, there was a-- a day off work.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "She had also a day off.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We used to-- they had a telephone and-- and-- where my wife was working, this family, they had a telephone.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They were Germans.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
